.”
</materialsCitation>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFE96A56F7F197F117E5B9BC" pageId="18" pageNumber="776" type="discussion">
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFE96A56F7F197F1174BBAFB" authorityName="Aellen" authorityYear="1959" box="[2061,2379,424,457]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Pipustrellus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="18" pageNumber="776" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="inexspectatus">Pipustrellus inexspectatus</taxonomicName>
is probably closest to the 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFE96A56F78C978916DFBAC3" baseAuthorityName="Kuhl" baseAuthorityYear="1817" box="[2160,2271,464,497]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="776" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="kuhlii">P. kuhlii</taxonomicName>
group of species. Records previously attributed to it from 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFE96A56F63597AE145CB92A" box="[2505,2652,503,536]" name="Democratic Republic of the Congo" pageId="18" pageNumber="776">DR Congo</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFE96A56F7B3944716A5B90D" box="[2127,2213,542,575]" name="Kenya" pageId="18" pageNumber="776">Kenya</collectingCountry>
are now attributed to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFE96A56F60C94471693B955" baseAuthorityName="Hill" baseAuthorityYear="1968" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="776" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eisentrauti">Hypsugo eisentrauti</taxonomicName>
. Specific epithet is often misspelled as inexpectatus. Monotypic.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
