<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFE96A56FA5690BF1433BC64" pageId="18" pageNumber="776" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFE96A56FA5690BF1433BC64" blockId="18.[1448,2656,740,1998]" pageId="18" pageNumber="776">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFE96A56FA5690BF190CBC35" bold="true" box="[1450,1804,1766,1799]" pageId="18" pageNumber="776">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Virtually nothing is known about ecology of Aellen’s Pipistrelle. Known distribution is veryscattered, and additional collecting efforts are needed to clarify its conversation status.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
